paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted information on KCNH2 variants, including penetrance data and individual records.

individual_records.evidence_sentence: Four mutants including N681I, D837G, R752W, and R823W can be purified from E. coli.
Six out of the 10 mutants were demonstrated to be insoluble when they were expressed in E. coli.

functional_data.summary: Mutations in KCNH2 can cause LQT2 and several disease-related mutations have been identified in the CNBHD.

variants.additional_notes: The N681I mutation is located at the binding interface with the eag domain.
